Word lists bundled in this directory:

english_words.txt
  Source: macOS system dictionary (/usr/share/dict/words)
  License: Public domain

chinese_words.txt
  Combined from two sources:

  1) THUOCL (THU Open Chinese Lexicon)
     URL: https://github.com/thunlp/THUOCL
     License: MIT License
     Copyright (c) 2018 THUNLP

  2) 现代汉语常用词表 (Modern Chinese Common Word List)
     URL: https://github.com/liangqi/chinese-frequency-word-list
     Source: Ministry of Education, PRC (教育部《现代汉语常用词表（草案）》)
     56,008 words from a 250-million-character corpus
     No explicit license declared in repository

  3) 12dicts-zh (Chinese Common Word List)
     URL: https://github.com/thiefstar/12dicts-zh
     License: CC0-1.0 (Public Domain)
     ~504K words compiled from CC-CEDICT, jieba, HanLP, and other sources

